Final scores please, without the bonus I gave you~ And feel free to enter even if you didn't say so before, yeah?

My score was 907, and then I went to bed. &hearts;

I asked a question, you losers gonna answer it?

Who do I have to beat up to win <i>this</i> tournament, and what's the prize? 

... You guys don't <i>look</i> like Zoanthropes, so it's just a regular fight? 'Cause that's just too easy, yeah? &hearts;
